      Constructor and Description
      InteractiveQuestionPanel(InteractiveQuestion IAQ, TopQuiz topquiz)
      Constructor for InterActiveQuestionPanel, displays all the content from the super class QuestionPanel, as well as a JPG file that is used for the interactive copmonent.
      MultipleChoiceQuestionPanel(MultipleChoiceQuestion MCQ, TopQuiz topquiz)
      Constructor for the MultipleChoiceQuestionPanel, displays the question as well as radio buttons with text answer options and a submit button.
      QuestionPanel(Question question, TopQuiz topquiz)
      Constructor for QuestionPanel super that displays the questions' text, submit button and a progress bar that serves as a timer.
      ShortAnswerQuestionPanel(ShortAnswerQuestion SAQ, TopQuiz topquiz)
      Displays all the content from the super QuestionPanel, and an extra textfield for the user to enter their response.
